text: Pimchanok Luevisadpaibul (; born 30 September 1992), nicknamed Baifern (; lit. "Fern Leaf"), is a Thai actress and model. She is best known for her lead role as Nam in the 2010 sleeper movie hit Crazy Little Thing Called Love with co- star Mario Maurer. She has been a freelance actress since 2016. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Thai actors
